Multiplatform

Stay connected anytime, anywhere. Whether you're at home, in the office, or a little of both, keep in touch with your community with our mobile-first design.

Gamification

Create a fun online experience that your members will love and return to. Our built-in gamification features let you engage with your users like never before.

Custom Reactions

Upload themed emojis or images for your users to interact with, all completely aligned with your brand.

Quests

Drive engagement by introducing fun challenges and rewards. New users can complete the Rookie Questline for a sweet level boost.

Badges

Foster a sense of pride and achievement in the community. Let members unlock badges for every completed questline.

Levels and Ranks

Recognize your community's biggest supporters, who are instrumental in keeping your community active and vibrant.

Profile Upgrades

Get access to cool upgrades that level up everyone's profile. Users can choose from a library of avatar frames and profile covers.

Safety

Leave your moderation problems behind. Beam.gg helps you keep your community safe with powerful moderation tools that protect your community from spam, abuse, and harmful content.

Member Roles

Scale your community with ease by assigning admins and moderators.

Audit Logs

See a list of all the moderation actions taken on your community platform.

Word Filter

Automatically filter content from your feed by blacklisting specific words from user posts and comments.

Member Reports

Empower members to keep the community safe by reporting users and content that violate community rules.
